title: Alien Contact - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 6/20/22

description:
George Noory and author Mark Gober explore his research into alien abductions, whether aliens are coming to Earth to conduct biological experiments on humans or even disrupt nuclear missile tests, and if stories of God in the Bible are actually chronicling visits by extra terrestrials.
